The paper deals with the efficiency of all-pay mechanisms in different auction environments, which is a topic that falls under game theory (cs.GT). The paper also involves the design of mechanisms and the analysis of their efficiency, which are topics that fall under distributed systems (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the price of anarchy, which is a concept in algorithmic game theory (cs.EC) and computational complexity (cs.CR).
